text: David Tomášek (born February 10, 1996) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for JYP Jyväskylä of the Liiga. Tomášek made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Pardubice during the 2015–16 Czech Extraliga season.
